heading: Mournfield Dungeon Guide
content: Mournfield is an incredibly quick dungeon for groups, as the second objective can be split farmed and completed by your party in no time flat. Barbarians can also acquire the . The monster families may present a challenge for some builds, especially because of the wide variety of enemies. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
